Source: vitos-dashboard
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: VITOS Team <vitos@vit.example>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: vitos-dashboard
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, vitos-base, vitos-monitor,
 python3 (>= 3.11), python3-fastapi, python3-uvicorn, python3-jinja2,
 python3-pam, python3-aiofiles, python3-multipart,
 python3-websockets, python3-weasyprint, tmux, ttyd, caddy, openssl
Description: VITOS web admin console (FastAPI + React)
 Replaces vitosctl with a browser-based admin dashboard. Tails the alert
 log via SSE, proxies live student terminals through ttyd, renders incident
 reports as PDF via weasyprint, and exposes a typed REST API over the
 vitos-busd event bus. PAM authentication against the vitos-admins group;
 LDAP support arrives in SP6.
